gged should have) and several other group cures from other classes I cannot name because I don't what they are but I know they exist :) all cure mark of death with no difficulty, why spend the 46 AAs (you need EB5 and WoP3) you would need for a CHANCE at a cure in time?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
